        <p style="margin-top:3px"><span style="font-size:9.5px; color:$ink;"><strong>PROMETOR</strong></span><span style="font-size:8.5px; color:$body;"> — verifier adversarial efêmero (contexto zero) · </span><span style="font-size:9.5px; color:$ink;"><strong>CRÍTICO</strong></span><span style="font-size:8.5px; color:$body;"> — review pedagógico (o PORQUÊ) · </span><span style="font-size:9.5px; color:$ink;"><strong>GALILEU</strong></span><span style="font-size:8.5px; color:$body;"> — benchmarks (N≥10, CV&lt;20%) · </span><span style="font-size:9.5px; color:$ink;"><strong>ATENA</strong></span><span style="font-size:8.5px; color:$body;"> — quality gate composto + AIDI (DORA proibido como proxy)</span></p>
