        <p style="margin-top:3px"><span style="font-size:9.5px; color:#FFFFFF;"><strong>MAESTRO</strong></span><span style="font-size:8.5px; color:#D8DDE3;"> — opera a state machine e despacha workers; coordena, NÃO produz · </span><span style="font-size:9.5px; color:#FFFFFF;"><strong>CRONOS</strong></span><span style="font-size:8.5px; color:#D8DDE3;"> — scheduler, dono único de cada cron</span></p>
  - elementId: r-head
